Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.73,0:01:36.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天气真好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.76,0:01:39.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 很适合猫猫们睡午觉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.65,0:01:42.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种天气也很适合看书
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.23,0:01:48.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跑到户外玩个痛快才是正道啦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.20,0:01:49.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好想出去玩的说
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.87,0:01:52.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 你有什么打算
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.60,0:01:54.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这 个 嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.37,0:01:56.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去了再说～
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.84,0:01:59.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃 恭介去求职了?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.95,0:02:01.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上到现在都没看到他人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.01,0:02:03.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 确实
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.51,0:02:06.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我转～
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.22,0:02:07.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有猫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.62,0:02:09.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,铃
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.43,0:02:15.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你的猫吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.69,0:02:17.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 我不认识
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.92,0:02:18.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别乱动哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.25,0:02:21.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 站住
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.66,0:02:26.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去哪边了?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.49,0:02:33.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呀 别蹭了啦 居然跑到校舍里来了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.64,0:02:34.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可没带猫粮
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.98,0:02:36.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笹濑川佐佐美!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.69,0:02:39.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那只猫莫非是笹濑川同学养的?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.22,0:02:41.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才不是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.61,0:02:42.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.99,0:02:44.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是它很黏你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.05,0:02:48.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都说不是了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.93,0:02:49.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.79,0:02:52.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我讨厌猫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.04,0:02:55.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佐酱
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.86,0:02:57.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神北同学!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.64,0:03:01.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佐酱?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.88,0:03:08.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,棗铃 你给我记住了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.33,0:03:12.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我每次都纳闷 她到底想让我记啥
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.48,0:03:19.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来你和笹濑川同学很要好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.35,0:03:22.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思 一直瞒着你们
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.60,0:03:27.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佐酱很怕羞 她让我不要到处乱讲
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.48,0:03:28.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你们俩在照料它吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.16,0:03:32.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 它一开始相当衰弱
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.92,0:03:34.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是佐酱发现了它…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.05,0:03:40.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,饭在这边哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.92,0:03:45.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它没饿吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.09,0:03:46.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那猫…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.34,0:03:48.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它怎么啦?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.51,0:03:51.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…感觉它有些疲软
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.69,0:04:15.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喔 你醒啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.05,0:04:24.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看你睡得那么香 莫非梦到美丽的肌肉了?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.07,0:04:33.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是个孤独异常的梦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.29,0:04:36.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被抛弃 流着泪的…某人的梦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.13,0:04:39.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的记忆?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.13,0:04:40.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.05,0:04:47.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃 喂 你干啥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.42,0:04:51.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么啦 肚子饿了?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.40,0:04:56.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听不懂…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.85,0:05:00.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很抱歉帮不到你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.05,0:05:04.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不能跟我回去的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.15,0:05:10.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪来的猫?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.92,0:05:15.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你被黏上了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.78,0:05:17.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这倒不是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.28,0:05:20.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小心别被宿管发现哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.12,0:05:27.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想进去?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.08,0:05:33.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪来的猫?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.71,0:05:36.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它硬要跟来…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.05,0:05:45.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喔 这是只母猫
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.35,0:05:50.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肉球…!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.32,0:05:54.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,进来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.79,0:05:56.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别动 让我帮你瞧瞧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.45,0:05:57.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唉 你真强硬…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.95,0:06:03.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们二位在干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.64,0:06:05.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,理树要强行…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.77,0:06:07.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说了别乱动
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.34,0:06:10.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直枝同学强上井之原同学…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.68,0:06:13.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这也太有违纲纪了…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.63,0:06:18.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那啥 我只是帮他看看有没伤到眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.27,0:06:25.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喝了这个就能得到Mega肌肉了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.47,0:06:28.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错 两人一起就是Giga肌肉了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.33,0:06:29.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦～Giga～
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.91,0:06:30.55,Comment,NTP,0,0,0,,耶耶～
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.59,0:06:31.57,Comment,NTP,0,0,0,,耶耶～
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.11,0:06:31.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,库特想看的是这本吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.92,0:06:32.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.69,0:06:36.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思 明明都借给直枝同学了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.62,0:06:38.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事 我现在也…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.62,0:06:40.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们也喝吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.70,0:06:44.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人称「俺制肌肉运动者2nd」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.67,0:06:47.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有股炸肉排的香味 或许意外的好喝哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.92,0:06:49.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,免了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.65,0:06:52.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我怕喝了变不回原样…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.70,0:06:53.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.53,0:06:55.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么我们这就喝喝看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.06,0:06:56.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,搞起!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.43,0:07:05.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那只猫…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.71,0:07:09.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 是我想多了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.59,0:07:18.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,醒醒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.75,0:07:20.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,醒醒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.35,0:07:24.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快醒醒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.75,0:07:25.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.58,0:07:29.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笹濑川同学啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.92,0:07:31.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃 你怎么在!?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.46,0:07:33.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘘 太大声了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.88,0:07:34.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.99,0:07:37.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 我还在做梦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.95,0:07:39.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是现实啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.29,0:07:42.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快给我清醒过来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.17,0:07:45.08,Comment,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛 痛痛痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.25,0:07:46.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吵什么 理树 有谁在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.93,0:08:07.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笹濑川同学…变猫了?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.52,0:08:11.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底怎么了嘛 尿肌肉了?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.53,0:08:15.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是猫啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.07,0:08:17.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是笹濑川同学
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.62,0:08:18.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.55,0:08:20.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这猫是笹濑川同学
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.43,0:08:24.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喔?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.88,0:08:27.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,头好痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.38,0:08:31.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么变成猫了 能恢复原状吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.96,0:08:33.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你刚才变回去了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.30,0:08:42.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过啊 就算你说它是笹濑川 不亲眼确认我还是很难相信
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.84,0:08:44.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘿咻
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.50,0:09:00.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然连续羞辱我两次 两次啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.64,0:09:02.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 变回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.66,0:09:04.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃 咦?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.55,0:09:05.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我变回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.48,0:09:07.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是怎么回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.90,0:09:09.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还想问呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.15,0:09:13.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.87,0:09:16.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃 你不怕再变成猫吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.83,0:09:20.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有点惦记室友 而且…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.05,0:09:23.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么晚还留在男生宿舍有点…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.88,0:09:25.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种非常时刻你还在意这个啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.01,0:09:28.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个超级重要好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.67,0:09:29.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.65,0:09:31.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来你相当爱管闲事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.93,0:09:36.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过你确实帮到我了 谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.82,0:09:38.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.39,0:09:39.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 你保重…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.65,0:09:45.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃 笹濑川同学!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.11,0:09:47.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又来了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.72,0:09:49.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我就说嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.56,0:09:52.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也没办法啊 总不能一直待在这里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.90,0:09:53.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.52,0:09:55.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.91,0:09:57.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我能听懂…你说的话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.39,0:10:03.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先不管我怎么突然听得懂猫语了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.15,0:10:05.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.13,0:10:07.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我为什么会变成猫啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.32,0:10:11.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恭介眼下不在 得由我想办法
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.65,0:10:13.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,任务开始
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.86,0:10:17.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笹濑川同学 我们先整理一下目前的情报吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.98,0:10:19.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啥?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.77,0:10:23.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…笹濑川同学变成猫是在…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.42,0:10:24.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真人醒来时
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.40,0:10:26.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出阳台时
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.43,0:10:31.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恢复原状是在真人失去意识时以及…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.58,0:10:34.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么说元凶就是这个邋遢的肌肉团子对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.18,0:10:37.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还不确定啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.01,0:10:38.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,另外…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.23,0:10:41.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这点我很有把握
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.24,0:10:44.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你大概是一出这个房间就会变成猫
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.31,0:10:49.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看你从阳台回到这个房间后就变回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.62,0:10:50.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,换言之…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.78,0:10:53.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我出不了这个房间了?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.75,0:10:56.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是说我到查清缘由为止要一直住在这个房间里?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.14,0:10:58.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 我可没这么说…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.03,0:11:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都一样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.37,0:11:05.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我凭什么非得和你们一起住在这个邋遢的男生宿舍里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.65,0:11:08.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吵耶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.14,0:11:15.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人家话还没说完…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.25,0:11:19.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肌肉滚出去!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.11,0:11:26.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 我也不想的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.34,0:11:31.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哼 你在肌肉与黑猫这两者中选了后者 仅此而已
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.36,0:11:36.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肌肉很机智 退身保友情
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.36,0:11:36.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs21}※日语「筋肉(肌肉)」「筋を通す(贯彻自身的正义)」都含筋字 冷笑话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.83,0:11:38.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打起精神来啊 真人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.69,0:11:41.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了 真人你还有肌肉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.06,0:11:44.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开朗地用你的肌肉一笑了之嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.65,0:11:47.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你…还肯和我一起玩肌肉吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.73,0:11:48.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.96,0:11:51.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看 肌肉肌肉～
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.08,0:11:56.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没办法啊 那咱们就暂时分隔两地吧肌肉!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.56,0:11:58.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 再会了肌肉!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.45,0:12:02.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,理树果然最赞了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.29,0:12:05.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yahoo! 理树最赞! 肌肉最赞!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.94,0:12:08.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不不 真人最赞
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.30,0:12:09.25,Comment,NTP,0,0,0,,不 理树…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.17,0:12:09.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,俩傻瓜…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.62,0:12:13.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可以用真人的床了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.76,0:12:16.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我 才 不 要
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.48,0:12:18.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先不谈这个 能把手机借我下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.21,0:12:21.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想知会一下室友
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.77,0:12:28.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 您好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.38,0:12:32.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么又来了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.05,0:12:35.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,理树君 怎么啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.85,0:12:37.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神北同学 是我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.07,0:12:38.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喵?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.31,0:12:42.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喵喵?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.84,0:12:43.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小毬同学?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.95,0:12:44.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 理树君
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.32,0:12:46.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你养猫啦?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.80,0:12:48.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她果然没听懂
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.77,0:12:51.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笹濑川同学让我带个话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.07,0:12:53.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她今天回不去了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.48,0:12:55.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.80,0:12:57.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,情况比较复杂
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.10,0:13:01.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佐酱怎么啦 不是病了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.73,0:13:03.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是 你放心
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.68,0:13:05.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.42,0:13:06.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她现在和你一起吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.15,0:13:10.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 她今天估计要在男生宿舍过夜了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.93,0:13:12.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.14,0:13:18.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那那那…佐酱和理树君现在不就是深夜幽会中吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.26,0:13:21.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,换我听
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.74,0:13:27.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少废话 赶紧洗了睡!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.77,0:13:32.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然只能听到「喵」 不过对不起!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.41,0:13:38.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,换洗衣物用这些行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.75,0:13:40.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.35,0:13:43.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉有点像同居呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.50,0:13:44.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什…同居!?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.32,0:13:47.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那啥 我就说说看啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.45,0:13:48.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.61,0:13:50.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真不要?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.66,0:13:52.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我干脆不换衣服了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.15,0:13:53.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.88,0:13:55.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说不换就不换!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.56,0:13:57.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那晚安吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.05,0:14:02.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太悲剧了…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.49,0:14:07.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么在我眼前就不变身呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.26,0:14:09.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且变成猫也能沟通
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.91,0:14:13.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么…只有我…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.94,0:14:22.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之我先去找找肯帮忙的人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.28,0:14:23.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.97,0:14:25.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麻烦你看家咯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.05,0:14:26.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,站住
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.32,0:14:30.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发梢…翘起来了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.21,0:14:44.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.27,0:14:46.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.62,0:14:49.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是受不了翘发而已
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.65,0:14:51.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你快去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.72,0:14:53.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 我出门了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.05,0:15:00.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.41,0:15:02.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喔 早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.50,0:15:04.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 我看不见前面了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.28,0:15:07.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猫的事果然还是该问铃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.22,0:15:10.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,铃 你午休时有空吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.34,0:15:17.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给 猫罐头哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.71,0:15:23.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,棗铃 你是有多瞧不起我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.32,0:15:25.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要我挠下巴?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.97,0:15:28.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别碰我!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.09,0:15:30.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,淡定 淡定
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.55,0:15:32.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没办法 那我回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.51,0:15:34.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么快?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.20,0:15:38.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啧啧啧 这事不能急
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.38,0:15:45.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来她没听懂你说的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.78,0:15:49.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才不稀罕她来帮我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.97,0:15:52.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有 这是闹哪样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.97,0:15:55.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你都变猫了 吃这个比较合理嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.42,0:15:57.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来是你的主意…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.63,0:16:01.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赶紧给我去小卖部买三明治和红茶!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.03,0:16:09.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好吃吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.68,0:16:14.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会 只是一想到我居然在过这种家里蹲生活…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.78,0:16:17.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就越来越想哭
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.91,0:16:20.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呀 别这么消沉嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.70,0:16:24.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…笹濑川同学很厉害的呀
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.06,0:16:29.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看 咱们学校垒球社那么强 而你一年级时就成了正式社员
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.95,0:16:32.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其他还有很多 比如很受后辈们爱戴
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.48,0:16:37.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对啊 我可是垒球社的希望和王牌
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.88,0:16:44.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拥有经受了无数的悔恨和痛苦磨练出的良好心理素质
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.62,0:16:54.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然差点在这点小状况上受挫 简直可耻
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.15,0:16:57.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拍了两句马屁就振作起来了…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.22,0:17:02.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事已至此 就算是猫也无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.56,0:17:08.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直枝理树 先一起找到能听懂我说话的人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.17,0:17:13.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猫猫 你好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.79,0:17:15.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.05,0:17:17.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 鞠躬了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.05,0:17:20.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好聪明的猫猫呀
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.47,0:17:27.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 这猫咪貌似很好摸的说
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.33,0:17:30.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乖乖 乖乖
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.44,0:17:32.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别随便摸我!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.01,0:17:39.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们几个 是我 我是笹濑川
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.88,0:17:48.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真够绝望的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.12,0:17:49.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.28,0:17:53.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,理树君
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.45,0:17:55.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小毬同学…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.52,0:17:58.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 猫猫也在
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.38,0:17:59.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乖乖
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.57,0:18:02.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说 神北同学…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.75,0:18:04.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佐酱还回不来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.91,0:18:10.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然理树君说她没事 我还是有些担心
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.37,0:18:16.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小毬同学
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.97,0:18:19.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望你能认真听完我接下来要说的话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.35,0:18:25.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是佐酱吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.90,0:18:28.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错 是我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.88,0:18:31.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,提问
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.11,0:18:34.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有种饮料佐酱常买
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.13,0:18:37.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有车站前那台自动售货机有卖
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.85,0:18:40.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佐酱习惯一次买几瓶呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.15,0:18:47.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,答对了 你真是佐酱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.08,0:18:53.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神北同学 我感受到了和你的深厚友谊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.58,0:18:54.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她说什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.05,0:18:57.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感受到了和你的深厚友谊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.74,0:19:04.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放心吧 无论佐酱变成什么样我们都是朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.64,0:19:09.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佐酱就拜托理树君啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.64,0:19:12.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也会尽力帮忙的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.53,0:19:14.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.56,0:19:16.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小事一桩啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.60,0:19:19.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天见
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.23,0:19:27.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,库特公今天也很好转呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.33,0:19:34.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小毬酱难道睡过头了?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.31,0:19:36.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事 还有一会儿才上课呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.14,0:19:47.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小毬同学是请假了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.99,0:19:51.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我拿午饭来了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.01,0:19:54.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.09,0:19:57.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要进来先敲门啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.61,0:20:01.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这换洗衣物是哪来的?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.71,0:20:02.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神北同学拿来的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.98,0:20:09.09,Comment,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs21}我把佐酱的洋服拿来了。要和睦相处哦。小毬
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.25,0:20:06.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,似乎正好在我出门后拿来的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.21,0:20:08.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小毬同学来过了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.30,0:20:11.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说 你单独跑出去了?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.22,0:20:15.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有很多事必须出去才能做嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.52,0:20:17.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 是出去方便了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.46,0:20:18.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请进吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.15,0:20:21.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她真是挺上心的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.15,0:20:24.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不换衣服始终不太舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.15,0:20:29.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说来你每次变回来总是有穿衣服对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.51,0:20:32.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.51,0:20:38.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打个比方 电影里偶尔会出现能让人变异的药物对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.73,0:20:42.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,变身后如果体积变大通常会撑破衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.07,0:20:44.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可为什么你的衣服就不会破呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.55,0:20:46.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想脱光我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.05,0:20:49.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不不不 我不是这个意思
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.80,0:20:54.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一般来说 衣服随身体一起发生变化很不自然吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.85,0:20:57.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个…确实
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.65,0:20:59.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 太非现实了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.42,0:21:03.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以大概…根本就不是现实
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.47,0:21:05.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就和那时一样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.92,0:21:10.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们所在的是一个可能发生这种怪事的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.22,0:21:12.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.27,0:21:14.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想啊 这就是件彻头彻尾的怪事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.03,0:21:16.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人根本不可能变成猫
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.21,0:21:20.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以真正诡异的其实是容忍这种事发生的这个世界
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.30,0:21:26.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是说我们误入了你说的这个诡异的世界?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.59,0:21:28.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.75,0:21:31.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你…你漫画看多了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.45,0:21:34.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么可能有这种事…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.16,0:21:37.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小毬酱不见了!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.40,0:21:41.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小毬酱…不见了…
