Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.90,0:23:40.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,0)\an6\pos(779,341)\bord2\1c&HFFFFFF&\fsp4}某人祈愿中的小小世界
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.10,0:23:34.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这异变到底是谁造成的?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.70,0:23:36.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个嘛 也就是说笹佐佐…
